Package: eatDB
Type: Package
Title: Spreadsheet Interface for Relational Databases
Version: 0.3.6
Authors@R: person("Benjamin", "Becker", email = "b.becker@iqb.hu.berlin.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: eatDB allows the creation and use of SQLite3 as a database system for data storage and usage via a complete R interface, treating the data as if it was a single spreadsheet.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports: DBI, RSQLite
RoxygenNote: 7.0.2
Suggests: testthat
